{"id":296,"ayahs":[{"number":21,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ أَعْثَرْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ لِيَعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنَّ وَعْدَ ٱللَّهِ حَقٌّۭ وَأَنَّ ٱلسَّاعَةَ لَا رَيْبَ فِيهَآ إِذْ يَتَنَٰزَعُونَ بَيْنَهُمْ أَمْرَهُمْ ۖ فَقَالُوا۟ ٱبْنُوا۟ عَلَيْهِم بُنْيَٰنًۭا ۖ رَّبُّهُمْ أَعْلَمُ بِهِمْ ۚ قَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ غَلَبُوا۟ عَلَىٰٓ أَمْرِهِمْ لَنَتَّخِذَنَّ عَلَيْهِم مَّسْجِدًۭا","translation":"AND IN THIS way have We drawn [people's] attention to their story, so that they might know - whenever they debate among themselves as to what happened to those [Men of the Cave] that God's promise [of resurrection] is true, and that there can be no doubt as to [the coming of] the Last Hour. And so, some [people] said: \"Erect a building in their memory; God knows best what happened to them.\" Said they whose opinion prevailed in the end: \"Indeed, we must surely raise a house of worship in their memory!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2161.mp3","surahId":18,"words":[{"id":23497,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23498,"position":2,"arabic":"أَعْثَرْنَا","translation":"আমরা জানিয়ে দিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23499,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","translation":"সম্পর্কে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23500,"position":4,"arabic":"لِيَعْلَمُوٓا۟","translation":"যেন তারা জানে","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23501,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23502,"position":6,"arabic":"وَعْدَ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23503,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌র","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23504,"position":8,"arabic":"حَقٌّۭ","translation":"সত্য","audioUrl":"wbw/018_021_008.mp3","charTypeName